/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="3381dcd6-93b0-4214-91d0-5235cf5fc588"><source>Smart PV Assistant</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Smart PV Assistant</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Slimme PV-assistent</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="1"><sdl:rep id="/Y13l0mmWLcFgxevFzQrEWHDJH0=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">/Y13l0mmWLcFgxevFzQrEWHDJH0=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="c80308ae-4927-4e42-bece-e836ee8677ef"><source>Overview</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Overview</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Overzicht</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="2"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">XTbMBHVY+t4kDGfkGlrAAQ0eIPU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="b38902f1-1906-4b26-a10b-7723e3bc2e41"><source>Smart PV Assistant has learned a vast amount of solar energy knowledge.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">Smart PV Assistant has learned a vast amount of solar energy knowledge.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">Smart PV Assistant has learned a vast amount of solar energy knowledge.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="3" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">dY3SEqQ5mrGDRz4lbFUctV8MkQ4=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="75f7a6bf-7954-4d4e-943c-b0565fb681a3"><source>Based on the large model and user scenarios, it is able to provide high-quality Q&amp;A services to solve usage problems and improve energy utilization, and provide users with more professional and thoughtful services, achieving more intelligent and efficient experience.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Based on the large model and user scenarios, it is able to provide high-quality Q&amp;A services to solve usage problems and improve energy utilization, and provide users with more professional and thoughtful services, achieving more intelligent and efficient experience.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Based on the large model and user scenarios, it is able to provide high-quality Q&amp;A services to solve usage problems and improve energy utilization, and provide users with more professional and thoughtful services, achieving more intelligent and efficient experience.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="4" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">POq/DWV5ziyIzcEp07Noow0/Sx0=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="6c19ee09-0ede-48f2-91b2-df47f85d5b6e"><source>Usage Instruction</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Usage Instruction</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Gebruiksinstructies</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="5"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">KGo9utCDqBXkmKdYzs0WMdPXbmI=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d4edce8c-2880-4899-92d0-2a8f13f21a0c"><source>After Smart PV Assistant is enabled, the floating bubble (<x id="0" />) is displayed on any screen of the app.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">After Smart PV Assistant is enabled, the floating bubble (<x id="0" />) is displayed on any screen of the app.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">After Smart PV Assistant is enabled, the floating bubble (<x id="0" />) is displayed on any screen of the app.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">xD3QLjcRvUBLf69s9YKPoHGjNO4=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="f4cfbec4-d628-4301-8472-fa07ed12dd77"><source>Tap the floating bubble to access the home screen of Smart PV Assistant for Q&amp;A.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">Tap the floating bubble to access the home screen of Smart PV Assistant for Q&amp;A.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">Tap the floating bubble to access the home screen of Smart PV Assistant for Q&amp;A.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">nlCpi6I514I3x+yfmsAPwpmuS8I=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="76803c25-e01c-48fc-9d0c-72f8b1b57684"><source>Enter your question in the dialog box, for example, <g id="3">Charge the ESS during the day and discharge it at night</g>.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">Enter your question in the dialog box, for example, <g id="3">Charge the ESS during the day and discharge it at night</g>.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">Enter your question in the dialog box, for example, <g id="3">Charge the ESS during the day and discharge it at night</g>.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="8" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">fKFE0GzaimUcOE5/clqbmLezvcU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="618dd9ed-a3a8-4b89-98ec-d0ee638fae6f"><source>Tap <x id="4" /> to send the question.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">Tap <x id="4" /> to send the question.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">Tap <x id="4" /> to send the question.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="9" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">4Qu5I3WWbMzr3jw0lTu5HZstG+M=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="041a65ed-0822-4538-b641-d0ebd85a8926"><source>A message indicating that the system is thinking will be displayed.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">A message indicating that the system is thinking will be displayed.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">A message indicating that the system is thinking will be displayed.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="10" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">9exDzqT0IoYbSHI/IHUwl2Kwkgw=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="695a2fab-f12d-40f9-b65d-a34d01ba430d"><source>After analysis, high-quality content will be output.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">After analysis, high-quality content will be output.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">After analysis, high-quality content will be output.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="11" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">nvi25Ht02b127bicAHcCu16uXVA=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="b4738879-55b8-4d47-a30d-3897d77fec00"><source>If <x id="5" /> is displayed in the info area on some screens, you can tap the text next to the icon to perform quick Q&amp;A.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">If <x id="5" /> is displayed in the info area on some screens, you can tap the text next to the icon to perform quick Q&amp;A.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">If <x id="5" /> is displayed in the info area on some screens, you can tap the text next to the icon to perform quick Q&amp;A.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="12" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">9bl1eN7Lzrtqq8ZwzFpTFuSRwzk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="bab20743-727f-4df4-ae45-266e08c92e6c"><source>At the top of the Smart PV Assistant screen, you can tap <x id="6" /> to create a new session<g id="10"> and tap <x id="8" /> to view historical Q&amp;A records</g>.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">At the top of the Smart PV Assistant screen, you can tap <x id="6" /> to create a new session<g id="10"> and tap <x id="8" /> to view historical Q&amp;A records</g>.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">At the top of the Smart PV Assistant screen, you can tap <x id="6" /> to create a new session<g id="10"> and tap <x id="8" /> to view historical Q&amp;A records</g>.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="13" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">MNwe3gzTn3G6JYWgDkG1lssivB0=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d6e4c719-2897-460c-9bf4-c0e4f307ed1c"><source>Under the answer generated by the Smart PV Assistant, there are buttons for copying (<x id="11" />), giving likes on (<x id="12" />), giving dislikes on (<x id="13" />), and complaining about (<x id="14" />) the answer.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">Under the answer generated by the Smart PV Assistant, there are buttons for copying (<x id="11" />), giving likes on (<x id="12" />), giving dislikes on (<x id="13" />), and complaining about (<x id="14" />) the answer.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">Under the answer generated by the Smart PV Assistant, there are buttons for copying (<x id="11" />), giving likes on (<x id="12" />), giving dislikes on (<x id="13" />), and complaining about (<x id="14" />) the answer.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="14" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">7s7UAZHwM7KyOhPBWgHKD9mlAFM=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></tran